  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:0",
      "text": "从 MaterialX Lama 开始学习。MaterialX Lama 是由 Industrial Light & Magic 开发的 production-ready material layering system。",
      "ascii_letters": 83,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:1",
      "text": "Lama Basics（Lama 基础课程入口）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:2",
      "text": "Lama Overview（Lama 概览课程入口）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:3",
      "text": "这节 intro 会概览即将学习的课程内容，主题是 Industrial Light & Magic 的 cutting-edge layered material system。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:4",
      "text": "Lama Surface（Lama Surface 节点基础课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:5",
      "text": "在本课中，我们会首先了解 MaterialX Lama Surface node，并说明它应如何作为所有 Lama layered materials 的 base 使用。",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:6",
      "text": "Lama Surface - 2 Sided（Lama Surface 双面材质课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:7",
      "text": "在第一课的基础上，我们会学习如何创建 two-sided Lama layered materials。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:8",
      "text": "Lama Diffuse（Lama Diffuse 漫反射构件课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:9",
      "text": "学习如何使用 Lama material networks 中这个 fundamental building block。",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:10",
      "text": "Lama Dielectric（LamaDielectric 介质材质课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:11",
      "text": "使用 LamaDielectric 创建 layer coatings、glass、plastics、diamonds，以及其他 materials。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:12",
      "text": "Lama Emission（Lama Emission 自发光材质课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:13",
      "text": "学习在 MaterialX Lama 中使用 material emission 的基础知识。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:14",
      "text": "Lama Sheen（Lama Sheen 绒面与织物效果课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:15",
      "text": "这节课会介绍 LamaSheen node，它通常用于模拟 cloth、velvet，或 dust layers。",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:16",
      "text": "Lama Conductor（LamaConductor 金属材质课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 26,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:17",
      "text": "在本课中，你将学习 LamaConductor node 的 fundamentals，以及如何用它创建美观且 realistic 的 metals。",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:18",
      "text": "Lama SSS（Lama SSS 次表面散射课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:19",
      "text": "在本课中，你将学习 LamaSSS 和 LamaTriColor nodes 的基础，用于模拟 subsurface scattering。这种效果在 candles、chocolate、skin，以及其他会 scatter light 的 surfaces 上都需要。",
      "ascii_letters": 84,
      "cjk_chars": 31
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:20",
      "text": "Lama Layer（Lama Layer 分层材质课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:21",
      "text": "在本课中，你将学习如何使用 Lama Layer node 作为 MaterialX Lama materials 的 building blocks。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:23",
      "text": "准备好进入 RenderMan Fundamentals learning path 的下一步了吗？",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9fe9a52878:24",
      "text": "让我们继续学习 RenderMan 随附、并由 Pixar Animation Studios 自己使用的 beautiful shaders。",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    }
  ],
